{"tid":1464282,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"不分化之餘要識得互相改善，呢種就係叫團結","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T17:08:04.000Z","uid":63382,"like":97,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"9d589fa0f501610c90157c89cc903deea897b4b6","tid":1464282,"uid":63382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:44:43.000Z","msg":"阻到人登機，就同旅客道歉<br />\n有旅客落機唔知去邊，就帶佢搭機鐵同巴士<br />\n我見現場都有好多人咁做，可以做多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先混亂有示威者同記者仲有醫護人員有衝突<br />\n無錯，你地成功阻止佢離開現場<br />\n做完硬手段就要做軟手段<br />\n軟手段就係道歉，而唔係捉鬼屌人呢啲無意思既野<br />\n呢種就係叫團結，不分化之餘要識得互相改善<br />\n你地要知道呢場運動已經去到國際層面<br />\n傳媒一個鏡頭影響力遠大於你塞鐵同塞馬路<br />\n唔好睇小和理非力量<br />\n<br />\n共勵之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f1266c5a56eee937da9de3867bac04f3582a56","tid":1464282,"uid":63382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e1c0836b1ab8a33417dc595f91032878dfe44c","tid":1464282,"uid":230890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:45:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c55d9f9657970f83e235a4bd75a22541e155e539","tid":1464282,"uid":63382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254c0220b969edba0d71130227a976c36705bd30","tid":1464282,"uid":63382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad701ce5fc71997bf74d1f9e3079b3ecaaca37a7","tid":1464282,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:47:15.000Z","msg":"721，推"},{"pid":"ec1cc60d0f5662da4fb132e8e448e0e34875d4fa","tid":1464282,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:47:21.000Z","msg":"<span s